span></h2>\n   <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">链接：</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"https://atsushisakai.github.io/PythonRobotics/\" target=\"_blank\">https://atsushisakai.github.io/PythonRobotics/</a></span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">本文介绍 PythonRobotics 的文档结构与定位，阐述该项目是一套基于 Python 的机器人算法代码与教材，提供获取方式、运行样例、贡献方式及文本阅读指南，并列出详细的模块索引与目录导航，帮助读者了解项目范围、技术栈以及如何参与贡献。</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"501968402\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.1128640776699028\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"824\" width=\"824\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=48c3b26e&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2Fg0kpxARkI2SuH9A1kc0JN9uMIiceCB0rVvSlZ6LLMt0UOEfG5ex13IqgAqicmlRbLpB5cfCDTSeqav4AYTcyO6ag%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:48px 8px 0em;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;clear:both;font-size:17px;min-height:1em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-cropsely2=\"65\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.11296296296296296\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;vertical-align: bottom;height: 65px;width: 578px;\" data-cropselx1=\